       <p style="text-align:justify;margin-bottom:5.000000pt;margin-top:5.000000pt;text-indent:35.450000pt"><img style="width:38.8mm; height:42.7mm" alt="" src="files/17/5fan_ru_86329_86d7e8f716a7ae0ab09a38ad3290d087.html_files/rId15.jpg" /></p>
